snippet.title: Sumorbit: A Planet Sumo Wrestling Game
snippet.description:
A physics based fighting game where planets sumo wrestle. Grab, throw, bounce and spin opponents out of the solar system.
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1653190/Sumorbit/
Website: https://sumorbit.com
Twitter: https://twitter.com/Sumorbit
Discord: https://discord.gg/Mc78SG86dC
Music by https://twitter.com/Oscarno_
